{"tid":318100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因為西門慶 我先識poly妹 多謝你 西門慶","createTime":"2017-07-12T01:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T01:29:57.000Z","uid":11512,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e9c248be52b6c0b3e2a5a14f2be9dd46cd09b7e","tid":318100,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"西門慶幫你儲好晒閃卡、每年重溫、連登又搵人起你底、搞鳩你<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B4ZsYWBuEk5ubHlfZW9NMmFoRk0?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F0B4ZsYWBuEk5ubHlfZW9NMmFoRk0%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=6NW41eiVfPN9Fm6qWJyIp0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e96857c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/0B4ZsYWBuEk5ubHlfZW9NMmFoRk0?usp=sharing</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n勸你立刻去報案、咩罪都唔緊要、報左先、你唔報、就等住變陳文緩<br />\n你都睇到佢既人生、唔係果幾張相、陳文緩一定嫁硬有錢佬、過闊西生活<br />\n如果你想成為下一個bobo既話、你就縮返入去個西度、當我乜都無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西門慶一定會改鳩你圖嫁、當正你係av女優、日日夜夜j鳩你、<br />\n<br />\n你d相一定會被佢貼街招、理大各憧有錢佬大樓已經有人發現你既街招、尋人當中呀<br />\n<br />\n你唔好放過鳩頭慶呀、佢好似已經搵人去左理大貼街招"},{"pid":"b03d889e498027bf04874be30f43cb250e2300ba","tid":318100,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:10:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"349d9070c3309263a6d2956d113059b4023ee928","tid":318100,"uid":48139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:11:15.000Z","msg":"條有擺明扮五毛實推post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6545acf61c6bb7519e7bf45da9ddb0f2fa2bd7","tid":318100,"uid":11512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條有擺明扮五毛實推post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真 出面淨係得西門慶啲POST先見到POLY妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本就係西門慶推尻POLY妹上報<br />\n如果POLY妹跳樓一定要拉尻西門慶<img src=\"/as